data.description: Amazing 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch home!  This home has it all!  New kitchen cabinetry and countertops, New stainless steel appliances included. All new Shaw LVP throughout,  Quartz countertops in bathrooms!  Check attached sheet for updates, too may to list!  Split bedroom floorplan.  Large master suite with walk-in closet.  Subway tile in master bath.  Formal dining, special occasions.  new concrete patio.  Beautiful private view.  Fenced backyard. Entire home like brand new!  Don't miss!
